All Classes

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ASTKCounter
    A class which walks through a compilation unit and counts the number of synchronized methods without a static keyword
    ASTKModifier
    A class which adds the static keyword to one synchronized method declaration in a compilation unit, represented by the mutationNumber stored in the MutationModifier superclass
    DataLog
    A class to log output data from the mutation testing to a text file
    DirectoryTestRunner
    Runs unit tests found within the user's unit test directory against objects found in the user's class directory
    EELOCounter
    A class which counts every unique swap of lock() MethodCallExpressions on objects within a compilation unit
    EELOModifier
    A class which performs unique swaps of lock() method call expressions within a compilation unit
    ELPALockCounter
    A class which walks through a compilation unit and counts double the number of lock, lockInterruptibly and tryLock method call expressions
    ELPALockModifier
    A class which replaces lock, lockInterruptibly and tryLock method call expressions with a different one of those three method call expressions in a compilation unit
    ELPASemaphoreCounter
    A class which walks through a compilation unit and counts double the number of acquire, acquireUninterruptibly and tryAcquire method call expressions
    ELPASemaphoreModifier
    A class which replaces acquire, acquireUninterruptibly and tryAcquire method call expressions with a different one of those three method call expressions in a compilation unit
    ESPCounter
    A class which walks through a compilation unit and counts the number of synchronized statements which are child nodes of other synchronized statements using different locks
    ESPModifier
    A class which swaps the locks between synchronized statements nested inside other synchronized statements in a compilation unit
    EXCRCounter
    A class to count the number of synchronized statements which have scope to expand the critical region to consume one statement above and one statement below the synchronized statement
    EXCRModifier
    A class to expand the critical region of a synchronized statement by one statement above and below the synchronized statement
    MBRCounter
    A class which walks through a compilation unit and counts the number of two parameter cyclic barrier object creation expressions there are
    MBRModifier
    A class which removes the optional runnable parameter from cyclic barrier method creation expressions in a compilation unit
    MD2TModifier
    A class which divides the time value of wait, await, sleep and join method call expressions by 2
    Movers
    A class containing methods suitable for moving statements and expressions in and out of synchronized statements
    MSFCounter
    A class which walks through a compilation unit and counts the number of semaphore objects created
    MSFModifier
    A class which changes the fairness of semaphores within a compilation unit
    MSPSystemOutCounter
    A class which walks through a compilation unit and counts the number of synchronized statements which do not use the "System.out" FieldAccessExpr as a lock
    MSPSystemOutModifier
    A class which changes the object inside the parentheses of a synchronized statement to "System.out" if the synchronized statement is not already using this as a lock
    MSPThisCounter
    A class which walks through a compilation unit and counts the number of synchronized statements which do not use the "this" keyword as a lock
    MSPThisModifier
    A class which changes the object inside the parentheses of a synchronized statement to "this" if the synchronized statement is not already using this as a lock
    MutationCounter
    An abstract superclass for all mutation counter classes
    MutationModifier
    An abstract superclass for all mutation modifier classes
    MutationWorker
    An abstract class with static methods which work through mutations
    MX2TModifier
    A class which multiplies the time value of wait, await, sleep and join method call expressions by 2
    MXCConstructorCounter
    A class which walks through a compilation unit and counts the number of semaphore latch and barrier objects created
    MXCConstructorDecModifier
    A class which decrements the initial values of barriers, latches and semaphores in a compilation unit
    MXCConstructorIncModifier
    A class which increments the initial values of barriers, latches and semaphores in a compilation unit
    MXCMethodCounter
    A class which walks through a compilation unit and counts the number of semaphore method calls which can be incremented or decremented in an MXC modification
    MXCMethodDecModifier
    A class which decrements the values of permits in semaphore method calls in a compilation unit
    MXCMethodIncModifier
    A class which increments the values of permits in semaphore method calls in a compilation unit
    MXTCounter
    A class which walks through a compilation unit and counts the number wait(), sleep(), join() or await() method calls
    RCXCCounter
    A class which walks through a compilation unit and counts the number of lock, unlock, signal, signalAll, acquire, release and countDown method call expressions
    RCXCModifier
    A class which removes lock, unlock, signal, signalAll, acquire, release and countDown method call expressions from a compilation unit
    RFUCounter
    A class which walks through a compilation unit and counts the number of occurrences of a finally block surrounding an unlock method call expression
    RFUModifier
    A class which removes the finally block around any unlock method call declaration in a compilation unit, represented by the mutationNumber stored in the MutationModifier superclass
    RFUModifier.FinallyContainsUnlockChecker
    A class which walks through a block statement and determines if at least one unlock method call expression exists.
    RJSCounter
    A class which walks through a compilation unit and counts the number of join method call expressions
    RJSModifier
    A class which replaces join method call expressions with an appropriately timed sleep expression in a compilation unit
    RNACounter
    A class which walks through a compilation unit and counts the number of notifyAll method call expressions
    RNAModifier
    A class which replaces notifyAll method call expressions with notify from a compilation unit
    RSBCounter
    A class which walks through a compilation unit and counts the number of synchronized statements
    RSBModifier
    A class which removes the synchronized part of a synchronized block in a compilation unit
    RSKCounter
    A class which walks through a compilation unit and counts the number of synchronized methods in the compilation unit
    RSKModifier
    A class which removes the synchronized attribute of one method declaration in a compilation unit
    RSTKCounter
    A class which walks through a compilation unit and counts the number of synchronized methods with a static keyword
    RSTKModifier
    A class which adds the static keyword to one synchronized method declaration in a compilation unit
    RTXCCounter
    A class which walks through a compilation unit and counts the number of wait, sleep, yield, notify and notifyall method call expressions
    RTXCModifier
    A class which removes wait, join, sleep, yield, notify and notifyAll method call expressions from a compilation unit
    RVKCounter
    A class which walks through a compilation unit and counts the number of volatile keywords
    RVKModifier
    A class which removes the volatile keyword from a field declaration in a compilation unit
    RXOBarrierCounter
    A class which walks calls on the RXOGenericCounter class with a set of object types relating to barriers
    RXOBarrierModifier
    A class calls upon the RXOGenericModifier class with a set of object type names relating to barriers
    RXOGenericCounter
    A class which walks through a compilation unit and counts the different concurrency mechanism objects instantiated and how many method calls are on each mechanism - the number of mutations stored is (mechanisms - 1)*methodCalls
    RXOGenericCounter.MechanismCounter
    An inner class which visits VariableDeclarators in a compilation unit and stores the different names of concurrency mechanisms it finds in the outer class' mechanism names list
    RXOGenericCounter.MethodCallCounter
    An inner class which walks through MethodCallExpressions in a compilation unit and stores the number of method calls relating to the concurrency mechanism name in the outer class' methodCalls parameter
    RXOGenericModifier
    A class which walks through a compilation unit and changes the concurrency mechanism object associated with a concurrency mechanism method call
    RXOGenericModifier.MechanismCounter
    An inner class which visits VariableDeclarators in a compilation unit and stores the different names of concurrency names it finds in the outer class' mechanism names list
    RXOGenericModifier.MethodCallCounter
    An inner class which walks through MethodCallExpressions in a compilation unit and stores the number of method calls relating to the mechanisms in the outer class' methodCalls parameter
    RXOLatchCounter
    A class which walks calls on the RXOGenericCounter class with a set of object types relating to latches
    RXOLatchModifier
    A class calls upon the RXOGenericModifier class with a set of object type names relating to latches
    RXOLockCounter
    A class which walks calls on the RXOGenericCounter class with a set of object types relating to locks
    RXOLockModifier
    A class calls upon the RXOGenericModifier class with a set of object type names relating to locks
    RXOSemaphoreCounter
    A class which walks calls on the RXOGenericCounter class with a set of object types relating to semaphores
    RXOSemaphoreModifier
    A class calls upon the RXOGenericModifier class with a set of object type names relating to semaphores
    SANCounter
    A class which walks through a compilation unit and counts double the number of getAndSet methods call expressions there are
    SANModifier
    A class which replaces getAndSet methods with a get method, then a set method in a compilation unit
    SHCRDownCounter
    A class to count the number of synchronized statements which have scope to move the critical region further down a parent child node list.
    SHCRDownModifier
    A class to shift the critical region of synchronized statements downwards by one statement
    SHCRUpCounter
    A class to count the number of synchronized statements which have scope to move the critical region further up a parent child node list.
    SHCRUpModifier
    A class to shift the critical region of synchronized statements upwards by one statement
    SKCRCounter
    A class to count the number of synchronized statements which have at least 3 child nodes and therefore the critical region can be reduced by one statement above and below the critical region.
    SKCRModifier
    A class to reduce the critical region of a synchronized statement by one statement above and below the synchronized statement
    SPCRCounter
    A class to count the number of synchronized statements which have at least 2 child nodes and therefore the critical region can be split.
    SPCRModifier
    A class to split the critical region of a synchronized statement
    Start
    The main implementation of the ConMuti program
    UserData
    A class to store the various paths on the user filesystem used by the program
